//@version=6
indicator(title="Quantum Bot — ICT Narrative Engine", shorttitle="QB ICT", overlay=true, max_bars_back=1500, max_labels_count=100, max_lines_count=100, max_boxes_count=60)

// ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
//   QUANTUM BOT — ICT NARRATIVE ENGINE
//   ──────────────────────────────────────
//   Pine Script v6  •  v2.3 — Multi-timeframe HTF context + REACTION-ZONE tiers
//
//   v2.3 ORB TEMPLATE (Opening Range Breakout — 7th template):
//     • Freezes the opening range of the chosen session (NY / London / Asian,
//       set per chart) over the first orbORMinutes, then watches for a breakout.
//     • Width filter (range ÷ ATR) skips too-wide (chop) / too-narrow (noise)
//       sessions — fires an ORB skip alert so you see what was filtered.
//     • HTF-gated entry style: breakout aligned with H1/H4 bias → IMMEDIATE
//       (tier A); counter / LTF-only → RETEST entry (tier B). One trade/session.
//     • Emits the standard payload (template "orb") → flows through the same
//       webhook/rules/execute/manage pipeline. NOTE: backend acceptedTemplates
//       must include "orb" or the signal will be filtered — backend patch pending.
//
//   v2.3 REACTION-ZONE GRADING (this build):
//     • Tier A = M15 setup sits at an HTF POI (OB/FVG matching trade dir)
//                AND aligned with HTF bias → with-trend. Full size/extension.
//     • Tier B = at an HTF POI but COUNTER to HTF bias → VALID, take it,
//                scalp to next zone / early partials (NOT vetoed).
//     • Tier C = open space, no HTF POI near → NO TRADE. Fires a non-trading
//                f_buildSkip() alert (action:"skip", no entry/sl/tp) so you
//                SEE what the HTF filter rejected. Backend forwards to Telegram.
//     • Trade payloads now carry action:"trade"; backend branches on action.
//
//   v2.3 HTF LAYER (additive — v2.2 detection stack untouched):
//     • H1/H4/Daily bias, FVG, OB, dealing-range from CONFIRMED bars only.
//     • Payload adds: activeSession, htfTier, htfBias, htfBiasAlign, htfConfluence.
//
//   v2.2 FIXES CARRIED IN:
//     • Near-edge (proximal-line) entries on SB/Unicorn/TurtleSoup/Judas/AM
//       (OTE stays deep-Fib by design). Fills on shallower retrace.
//     • Draw-clamp math.max(storedBar, bar_index-499) on FVG/OB/IFVG boxes.
//     • max_bars_back=500 ; impulseATR "0.00" JSON mask ; seeded webhook key.
//     • NOTE: NAS100→NDQ symbol mapping is a BACKEND (webhook.js) fix, not Pine.
//
//   v2.2: OTE Fib fallback removed (real-confluence only).
//   v2.1: IFVG primitive + Equal H/L + AM IFVG template.
//
// ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

// ─── INPUTS — VISIBILITY ─────────────────────────────────────────────

